title: [Feywrot Mire, Highland]
description: The decayed skeleton of a large cat rests half in and half out of a small brackish pool beside the main path.  Its jaw is frozen in a silent scream, and bits of leathered skin cling tenuously to its bones.  An odd growth of fungi clutters the surrounding area.
